text: A by-election was held for the New South Wales Legislative Assembly electorate of Alexandria on 18 May 1912, following the death of John Dacey. ==Results== ==See also== *Electoral results for the district of Alexandria *List of New South Wales state by-elections ==References== Category:1912 elections in Australia Category:New South Wales state by-elections Category:1910s in New South Wales Category:May 1912 events
title: 1912 Alexandria state by-election
